52	Servidumbre	Caso 1: Solicitud de retiro de infraestructura por presunta invasiónPetición (Parte 1)	(Input): El usuario exige el retiro urgente de una red de alta tensión instalada en su predio privado, argumentando que se colocó sin su permiso y viola su derecho constitucional a la propiedad y posesión.  Respuesta (Output): Se niega la solicitud de retiro. La argumentación central es que la red lleva en operación más de 17 años garantizando un servicio público esencial. Legalmente, esta infraestructura está amparada por la figura de servidumbre legal de conducción de energía, la cual se impone por ley y no requiere un acuerdo o reconocimiento individual previo con el propietario. Además, se consolida por el ejercicio material, continuo y público del derecho sin que el propietario haya presentado oposición jurídica oportuna en el pasado.	\N	2026-05-15 00:58:54.224398+00	[7.516995e-05,0.058622442,-0.07460726,-0.04881805,-0.014009509,0.017837731,0.0775835,0.03821553,-0.025446583,0.046181373,0.11347516,0.0066189915,-0.024387667,0.013556786,0.057870813,-0.0023556058,0.03449414,0.0048798462,-0.02438521,0.048023947,0.14734608,-0.018441008,-0.10101496,0.04649187,-0.13022424,-0.02335954,-0.028758619,0.00050424214,-0.08046205,-0.021423878,-0.0055463803,-0.017605687,0.07748467,-0.0357427,0.019013125,0.054678172,0.031429302,-0.107547484,-0.036931545,0.06732749,-0.07254455,-0.046608757,-0.09496373,-0.04444369,0.044975165,-0.06059268,0.026793415,0.0930053,0.013415292,-0.067821525,-0.03553816,-0.0067894673,-0.048069827,0.07027534,0.013488209,-0.04924939,-0.0091624465,-0.026797986,0.097054,-0.027986098,-0.03612604,0.029870529,-0.016837211,-0.004402238,0.062568784,-0.02653706,0.047045417,-0.020044036,-0.049846165,0.06009419,0.076929055,0.01839043,0.06352116,0.027849384,-0.013456699,0.05223777,-0.023411851,0.07215921,0.017081667,-0.07508431,0.085690565,-0.039483473,-0.027263524,-0.038848203,0.04123328,-0.042529225,-0.04851687,0.004732348,0.08882739,0.031018546,0.022149492,0.076569