54	Servidumbre	Caso 3: Orden de suspensión de trabajos en el predio (Parte 1)	Petición (Input): El usuario exige la suspensión inmediata de cualquier trabajo u obra relacionada con la red de alta tensión dentro de su propiedad, al menos hasta que se emita una respuesta de fondo a su petición.  \r\n\nRespuesta (Output): Se informa que los mantenimientos ya finalizaron, quedando pendiente únicamente labores de cierre y retiro de material viejo (mitigación), las cuales se detuvieron temporalmente por la solicitud del usuario. Sin embargo, se le aclara al usuario que la empresa tiene el deber legal (obligación) de realizar reparaciones, mantenimientos y reposiciones en las redes para garantizar la prestación segura del servicio público y salvaguardar la integridad de las personas.	\N	2026-05-15 00:59:58.592418+00	[0.0038935943,-0.012915713,-0.045091968,-0.036136024,-0.017035462,0.012972882,0.0733496,-0.002422409,0.019465921,0.015473221,0.12499828,0.042241316,-0.040498495,0.029896121,0.038443755,-0.04402079,-0.015668737,0.04949789,-0.06188451,0.055140592,0.12518659,-0.064787015,-0.07095937,0.06563903,-0.12968089,-0.0066498662,-0.025670575,-0.05842205,-0.048072305,-0.06504893,-0.011717792,0.008494137,0.079212815,-0.07234085,-0.035686176,0.0776726,0.045058593,-0.084667295,-0.043372266,0.039206285,-0.06233919,-0.076398365,-0.063656144,-0.05222504,-0.0069539803,-0.06467909,0.03816948,0.02665112,-0.04638796,-0.043231975,-0.010584748,-0.026211318,-0.002976337,0.08768029,0.009762648,-0.104121044,-0.015455008,-0.03247267,-0.009735886,-0.028571142,-0.035673015,-0.0108428085,-0.051475536,0.020652138,0.044363443,-0.017953489,-0.02958195,-0.042724144,-0.022503765,0.027230835,0.04334816,-0.06928696,0.021765504,0.018293407,-0.01262646,0.024443382,-0.035114154,0.10271923,0.048572134,-0.10381164,0.10351118,-0.006622004,-0.0052930093,0.029809488,-0.019054677,0.0083780615,-0.069562495,-0.012179542,0.062478714,0.06670669,0.026831511,0.051123608,0.036681186,-0.07417564,-0.07183599,-0.030095